'''Fela fa letshololo le simolotse ngwana, mo siele dino (e seng dino tagi)kgapetsa kgapetsa go feta jaaka gale go thibela tatlhegelo ya metsi mo mmeleng.'''<br />
'''Dingwe tsa dino tse di tshwanetseng ke'''<br />
* Kgodu ya setampa kgotsa ya raese, moro le dijo tse dingwe tse di metsi jaaka motogo wa ting.
* Mashi a lebele, dino tse di dirilweng ka mashi jaaka madila le yokate.
* Metsi a a phepa le matute a maungo.
* Motswako wa letshololo o o fiwang kwa kokelwaneng fa o le teng mo gae: '''Tlhakanya jaana:''' pakete ya ORS + lithara ya metsi a a bedileng a sena go tsidifala.<br />
'''Ela tlhoko''': Siela ngwana dino tse jaaka a batla.
